git clone https://github.com/akalinow/RootAnalysis
cd RootAnalysis
git checkout relevant_tag
cmake ./
make -j 4

In case problewm with cmake use alternative building procedure with configure:


git clone https://github.com/akalinow/RootAnalysis
cd RootAnalysis
git checkout relevant_tag
libtoolize
aclocal
automake --add-missing
autoreconf
./configure 
make
